%5Etfw">@WagnerLab_KCI</a> is out today in <a href="https://twitter.com/CellReports?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@CellReports</a> ! Learn the role of JAK1 kinase as a key signaling mediator of cytokines that promote mutant KRAS-induced pancreatic cancer initiation and progression. <a href="https://t.co/zYM6VAj72H">https://t.co/zYM6VAj72H</a><a href="https://twitter.com/karmanoscancer?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@karmanoscancer</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/waynestate?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@waynestate</a></p>&mdash; Hridaya (@hridayastha) <a href="https://twitter.com/hridayastha/status/1788954855010382018?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">May 10, 2024</a></blockquote> <script async="" src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script> </div> <h1 id="famsci-fusion-timeline">FamSci Fusion Timeline</h1> <div class="jekyll-twitter-plugin"><a class="twitter-timeline" data-width="500" data-tweet-limit="3" href="https://twitter.com/hridayastha?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">Tweets by hridayastha</a> <script async="" src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script> </div>]]></content><author><name></name></author><category term="sample-posts"/><category term="external-services"/><category term="formatting"/><summary type="html"><![CDATA[New research from the WagnerLab is out today in CellReports. Getting this work published in Cell Reports required incredible amount of work (7 main and 17 'supplemental' figures and 5 tables). Take a look and learn the role of JAK1 kinase as a critical signaling mediator of cytokines that promote mutant KRAS-induced pancreatic cancer initiation and progression.]]></summary></entry><entry><title type="html">A must-read article by David G. Drubin.</title><link href="https://hridayastha.github.io/blog/2023/redirect/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="A must-read article by David G. Drubin."/><published>2023-01-30T17:39:00+00:00</published><updated>2023-01-30T17:39:00+00:00</updated><id>https://hridayastha.github.io/blog/2023/redire